EN: We visit this ancient temple every year.

ZH: 寺庙的山门上刻着精美的石刻。
EN: The temple gate is decorated with exquisite stone carvings.

ZH: 寺庙里散发出一股神圣的气息。
EN: The temple exudes a sacred aura.

ZH: 这是一座宏伟的佛教寺庙。
EN: This is a grand Buddhist temple.

ZH: 在寺庙里，人们可以找到内心的平静。
EN: In the temple, people can find inner peace.

ZH: 这座寺庙的建筑风格独特。
EN: The architectural style of this temple is unique.

ZH: 每天都有很多信徒到寺庙祈福。
EN: Every day, many believers come to the temple to pray for blessings.

ZH: 寺庙的屋檐上挂着红灯笼。
EN: Red lanterns hang on the eaves of the temple.

ZH: 寺庙里的和尚都非常和蔼可亲。
EN: The monks in the temple are very kind.

ZH: 这座寺庙临海而建，景色宜人。
EN: This temple is built by the sea and has pleasant scenery.

ZH: 寺庙被青山环绕，景色优美。
EN: The temple is surrounded by green hills, creating beautiful scenery.

ZH: 这座寺庙是当地人的信仰中心。
EN: This temple is the center of local beliefs.

ZH: 寺庙的大殿内供奉着佛祖的塑像。
